[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    573[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The opening Priya-with-the-parking-question vignette earns its position as the chapter's strongest single articulation of the legacy-healthcare-chatbot-failure-mode.** The dermatology-appointment-on-Thursday-at-10-AM, the website-with-eleven-PDFs-three-of-which-are-dated-2019, the chat-bubble-that-says-Hi-can-I-help-you, the button-menu-that-does-not-contain-the-parking-option, the Monday-through-Friday-from-8-AM-to-5-PM with-please-leave-a-message at 7-PM-Tuesday cadence is the recipe's clearest articulation of the deflection-mechanism-that-does-not-deflect primitive that grounds the rest of the recipe.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    574[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "the metric the team that deployed it optimized for was 'containment rate,' which in practice meant 'the percentage of users who gave up before reaching a human'" framing earns its position** as the recipe's clearest articulation of the perverse-metric primitive that the chapter pedagogy depends on.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    575[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "the answer is in the practice's office manager's head. It is also written down somewhere, probably in a Word document on a shared drive, last updated two years ago. It might also be on the practice's printed patient handout, which is a tri-fold brochure that exists somewhere in a stack at the front desk" framing earns its position** as the recipe's clearest articulation of the institutional-knowledge-is-scattered primitive that grounds the corpus-curation-as-the-project Honest-Take observation.
