[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    581[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "Scope Containment: The Most Underweighted Discipline" subsection's three-layer defense-in-depth framing (system prompt, vendor-managed guardrails, offline scope-drift review) is the recipe's strongest single passage on the layered-scope-discipline primitive.** The "The reason the scope discipline is the make-or-break operational issue is that the LLM will, by default, attempt to answer almost any question. It is good at sounding helpful. The institution's job is to make it unhelpful in a specific, principled way: unhelpful about the things it should not help with, helpful about the things it should" framing is the recipe's clearest articulation of the unhelpful-in-a-principled-way primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    582[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "Why a Good FAQ Bot Builds the Operational Muscles for Everything Else" subsection's six-discipline enumeration is recipe-distinct and is the chapter's strongest single FAQ-bot-as-foundational-recipe primitive.** The "The institution that ships an FAQ bot well has, almost incidentally, built the operational substrate for every more-complex conversational AI product it will later build. The institution that ships an FAQ bot badly has built the substrate for shipping every later recipe badly too" framing earns its position as the chapter's strongest single foundational-recipe primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    583[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The Where-the-Field-Has-Moved subsection's seven-update enumeration with appropriate verify-at-build-time hedges is correctly elevated** and grounds the recipe in the 2026 state of the field including the build-vs-buy economics observation.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    584[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Self-deprecating expertise lands well throughout the Honest Take.** The "the failure modes are the most forgiving. It is also the recipe where institutions most consistently underinvest, because they assume the simplicity of the use case translates to simplicity of execution. It does not" framing is the recipe's clearest articulation of the institutional-underinvestment-trap primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    585[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The Honest Take's eight-trap enumeration is well-chosen.** Each trap is a real failure mode with a specific cause and a specific institutional remedy. The corpus-as-someone-else's-problem trap (first), the too-narrow-scope trap (second), the too-broad-scope trap (third), the crisis-detection-as-phase-two trap (fourth), the underweighting-the-persona trap (fifth), the no-quality-measurement trap (sixth), and the one-time-build trap (seventh) frame the recipe's central architectural primitives in priority order.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    586[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "the thing that surprises engineers coming from generic-chatbot backgrounds" / "the thing that surprises healthcare professionals coming from clinical-software backgrounds" cross-discipline-comparisons earn their position** as the recipe's clearest articulation of the unglamorous-pieces-are-the-engineering-value primitive ("the corpus curation. The scope rule definitions. The crisis vocabulary. The prompt versioning. The conversation logging and access controls. The per-cohort metric pipeline. The accessibility tuning of the chat widget. The disaster-recovery plan. The patient-rights workflow") and the patient-experience-is-load-bearing primitive ("the voice. The cadence. The empathetic phrasing for difficult moments. The willingness to say 'I don't know, let me get you to someone who does'").
